Package: Zcalc
Type: Package
Title: One-step installation of MOSAIC Calculus packages
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Daniel Kaplan
Maintainer: Daniel Kaplan <dtkaplan@gmail.com>
Description: There are several special-purpose packages associated with the MOSAIC Calculus project: mosaic, mosaicCalc, Znotes, Zdata, Zsandbox, Zapps, mosaicCalc. This package allows them all to be installed or loaded at once.
Requires:
    mosaicCalc (>= 0.5.6),
    rlang (>= 1.0.1)
Imports:
    mosaic,
    mosaicCore,
    ggformula,
    palmerpenguins,
    learnr,
    shiny,
    shinyjs, 
    rsconnect, 
    MMAC
Remotes:
    github::ProjectMOSAIC/mosaicCalc@beta
